# 🎙️ EchoCap

*Record and Save your favourite tracks*

EchoCap is a simple, browser-based audio recording application that captures system audio from your screen. Perfect for recording music, podcasts, or any audio playing on your computer.

## ✨ Features

- **System Audio Recording**: Captures audio from your screen/display
- **High Quality**: Records at 48kHz sample rate with 192kbps bitrate
- **Instant Download**: Automatically downloads recordings as WebM files
- **Clean Interface**: Simple, user-friendly design
- **Browser-Based**: No installation required - runs directly in your web browser

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
- Microphone/audio permissions

### Installation

1. Clone or download this repository
2. Open `index.html` in your web browser
3. Grant screen sharing permissions when prompted

### Usage

1. Click **"Start Recording"** to begin
2. Select the screen/application you want to record audio from
3. The app will capture the audio from your selected source
4. Click **"Stop Recording"** when finished
5. Your recording will automatically download as `recording.webm`

## 📁 Project Structure

```
echocap/
├── index.html      # Main HTML file
├── style.css       # Styling
├── script.js       # Recording functionality
└── README.md       # This file
```

## 🔧 Technical Details

- **Audio Format**: WebM with Opus codec
- **Sample Rate**: 48,000 Hz
- **Bitrate**: 192 kbps
- **Audio Processing**: Echo cancellation and noise suppression disabled for pure audio capture

## 🎯 Use Cases

- Recording music from streaming services
- Capturing podcast audio
- Saving audio from video calls or meetings
- Recording system sounds and notifications
- Creating audio samples from web content

## 🛠️ Customization

You can modify the recording settings in `script.js`:

```javascript
// Adjust audio quality
audioBitsPerSecond: 192000  // Change bitrate
sampleRate: 48000          // Change sample rate

// Modify file naming
a.download = 'recording.webm';  // Change filename
```

## 📱 Browser Support

| Browser | Support |
|---------|---------|
| Chrome  | ✅ Full |
| Firefox | ✅ Full |
| Safari  | ✅ Full |
| Edge    | ✅ Full |

## 🔒 Privacy

EchoCap runs entirely in your browser - no data is sent to external servers. All recordings are processed locally and downloaded directly to your device.

